audio_analysis.transcript: I'm ranking every survivor in Risk or Rain 2 to find out which is the best one. This is Commando, you're run of the mill, main character, pew pew shoot, bad guy, mysterious look and eh. He's about as basic as he can ask for in a game like this. And that's not a bad thing, he sets a good starting point which makes him a solid pick for new players. He's super simple to understand and is a great option to learn how items affect your arsenal. This does however make him kinda boring to play once you start unlocking more interesting characters. Like when I first unlocked Bandit, I barely touched Commando because Bandit is just that much more interesting in just about every way. But again, that doesn't make Commando a bad character. If you can even get a couple trytip daggers, you can really ruin a boss's day. If Commando was just yet another character to unlock, I would definitely put him lower down in the tier list. But he really does shine as a good starter character for beginners who are trying to learn the ropes. So for that reason, I'm going to put him in beat here.
